38static constexpr char kCodegenZoneName[] = "codegen-zone";
39static constexpr char kGraphZoneName[] = "graph-zone";
40static constexpr char kInstructionZoneName[] = "instruction-zone";
41static constexpr char kRegisterAllocationZoneName[] =
42 "register-allocation-zone";
43
44inline Maybe<OuterContext> GetModuleContext(OptimizedCompilationInfo* info) {
45 Tagged<Context> current = info->closure()->context();
46 size_t distance = 0;
47 while (!IsNativeContext(*current)) {
48 if (current->IsModuleContext()) {
49 return Just(OuterContext(
50 info->CanonicalHandle(current, current->GetIsolate()), distance));
51 }
52 current = current->previous();
53 distance++;
54 }
55 return Nothing<OuterContext>();
56}
57
58class PipelineData {
59 public:
60 // For main entry point.
61 PipelineData(ZoneStats* zone_stats, Isolate* isolate,
62 OptimizedCompilationInfo* info,
63 TurbofanPipelineStatistics* pipeline_statistics)
64 : isolate_(isolate),
65 allocator_(isolate->allocator()),
66 info_(info),
67 debug_name_(info_->GetDebugName()),
68 may_have_unverifiable_graph_(v8_flags.turboshaft),
69 zone_stats_(zone_stats),
70 pipeline_statistics_(pipeline_statistics),
71 graph_zone_scope_(zone_stats_, kGraphZoneName, kCompressGraphZone),
72 graph_zone_(graph_zone_scope_.zone()),
73 instruction_zone_scope_(zone_stats_, kInstructionZoneName),
74 instruction_zone_(instruction_zone_scope_.zone()),
75 codegen_zone_scope_(zone_stats_, kCodegenZoneName),
76 codegen_zone_(codegen_zone_scope_.zone()),
77 broker_(new JSHeapBroker(isolate_, info_->zone(),
78 info_->trace_heap_broker(),
79 info->code_kind())),
80 register_allocation_zone_scope_(zone_stats_,
81 kRegisterAllocationZoneName),
82 register_allocation_zone_(register_allocation_zone_scope_.zone()),
83 assembler_options_(AssemblerOptions::Default(isolate)) {
84 PhaseScope scope(pipeline_statistics, "V8.TFInitPipelineData");
85 graph_ = graph_zone_->New<Graph>(graph_zone_);
86 source_positions_ = graph_zone_->New<SourcePositionTable>(graph_);
87 node_origins_ = info->trace_turbo_json()
88 ? graph_zone_->New<NodeOriginTable>(graph_)
89 : nullptr;
90 simplified_ = graph_zone_->New<SimplifiedOperatorBuilder>(graph_zone_);
91 machine_ = graph_zone_->New<MachineOperatorBuilder>(
92 graph_zone_, MachineType::PointerRepresentation(),
93 InstructionSelector::SupportedMachineOperatorFlags(),
94 InstructionSelector::AlignmentRequirements());
95 common_ = graph_zone_->New<CommonOperatorBuilder>(graph_zone_);
96 javascript_ = graph_zone_->New<JSOperatorBuilder>(graph_zone_);
97 jsgraph_ = graph_zone_->New<JSGraph>(isolate_, graph_, common_, javascript_,
98 simplified_, machine_);
99 observe_node_manager_ =
100 info->node_observer()
101 ? graph_zone_->New<ObserveNodeManager>(graph_zone_)
102 : nullptr;
103 dependencies_ =
104 info_->zone()->New<CompilationDependencies>(broker_, info_->zone());
105 }

119 debug_name_(info_->GetDebugName()),
120 may_have_unverifiable_graph_(v8_flags.turboshaft_wasm),

122 pipeline_statistics_(pipeline_statistics),
123 graph_zone_scope_(zone_stats_, kGraphZoneName, kCompressGraphZone),
124 graph_zone_(graph_zone_scope_.zone()),
125 graph_(mcgraph->graph()),
126 source_positions_(source_positions),
127 node_origins_(node_origins),
128 machine_(mcgraph->machine()),
129 common_(mcgraph->common()),
130 mcgraph_(mcgraph),
131 instruction_zone_scope_(zone_stats_, kInstructionZoneName),
132 instruction_zone_(instruction_zone_scope_.zone()),
133 codegen_zone_scope_(zone_stats_, kCodegenZoneName),
134 codegen_zone_(codegen_zone_scope_.zone()),
135 register_allocation_zone_scope_(zone_stats_,
136 kRegisterAllocationZoneName),

138 assembler_options_(assembler_options) {
139 simplified_ = graph_zone_->New<SimplifiedOperatorBuilder>(graph_zone_);
140 javascript_ = graph_zone_->New<JSOperatorBuilder>(graph_zone_);
141 jsgraph_ = graph_zone_->New<JSGraph>(isolate_, graph_, common_, javascript_,
142 simplified_, machine_);
143 }

146 // For CodeStubAssembler and machine graph testing entry point.
147 PipelineData(ZoneStats* zone_stats, OptimizedCompilationInfo* info,
148 Isolate* isolate, AccountingAllocator* allocator, Graph* graph,
149 JSGraph* jsgraph, Schedule* schedule,
150 SourcePositionTable* source_positions,
151 NodeOriginTable* node_origins, JumpOptimizationInfo* jump_opt,
152 const AssemblerOptions& assembler_options,
153 const ProfileDataFromFile* profile_data)
154 : isolate_(isolate),
155#if V8_ENABLE_WEBASSEMBLY
156 // TODO(clemensb): Remove this field, use GetWasmEngine directly
157 // instead.
158 wasm_engine_(wasm::GetWasmEngine()),
159#endif // V8_ENABLE_WEBASSEMBLY
160 allocator_(allocator),
161 info_(info),
162 debug_name_(info_->GetDebugName()),
163 zone_stats_(zone_stats),
164 graph_zone_scope_(zone_stats_, kGraphZoneName, kCompressGraphZone),
165 graph_zone_(graph_zone_scope_.zone()),
166 graph_(graph),
167 source_positions_(source_positions),
168 node_origins_(node_origins),
169 schedule_(schedule),
170 instruction_zone_scope_(zone_stats_, kInstructionZoneName),
171 instruction_zone_(instruction_zone_scope_.zone()),
172 codegen_zone_scope_(zone_stats_, kCodegenZoneName),
173 codegen_zone_(codegen_zone_scope_.zone()),
174 register_allocation_zone_scope_(zone_stats_,
175 kRegisterAllocationZoneName),
176 register_allocation_zone_(register_allocation_zone_scope_.zone()),
177 jump_optimization_info_(jump_opt),
178 assembler_options_(assembler_options),
179 profile_data_(profile_data) {
180 if (jsgraph) {
181 jsgraph_ = jsgraph;
182 simplified_ = jsgraph->simplified();
183 machine_ = jsgraph->machine();
184 common_ = jsgraph->common();
185 javascript_ = jsgraph->javascript();
186 } else if (graph_) {
187 simplified_ = graph_zone_->New<SimplifiedOperatorBuilder>(graph_zone_);
188 machine_ = graph_zone_->New<MachineOperatorBuilder>(
189 graph_zone_, MachineType::PointerRepresentation(),
190 InstructionSelector::SupportedMachineOperatorFlags(),
191 InstructionSelector::AlignmentRequirements());
192 common_ = graph_zone_->New<CommonOperatorBuilder>(graph_zone_);
193 javascript_ = graph_zone_->New<JSOperatorBuilder>(graph_zone_);
194 jsgraph_ = graph_zone_->New<JSGraph>(isolate_, graph_, common_,
195 javascript_, simplified_, machine_);
196 }
197 }

218 ~PipelineData() {
219 // Must happen before zones are destroyed.
220 delete code_generator_;
221 code_generator_ = nullptr;
222 DeleteTyper();
223 DeleteRegisterAllocationZone();
224 DeleteInstructionZone();
225 DeleteCodegenZone();
226 DeleteGraphZone();
227 }

336 void ChooseSpecializationContext() {
337 if (info()->function_context_specializing()) {
338 DCHECK(info()->has_context());
339 specialization_context_ = Just(OuterContext(
340 info()->CanonicalHandle(info()->context(), isolate()), 0));
341 } else {
342 specialization_context_ = GetModuleContext(info());

387 void DeleteGraphZone() {

389 graph_zone_ = nullptr;
390 graph_ = nullptr;

392 node_origins_ = nullptr;
393 simplified_ = nullptr;
394 machine_ = nullptr;

397 jsgraph_ = nullptr;
398 mcgraph_ = nullptr;
399 schedule_ = nullptr;
400 graph_zone_scope_.Destroy();
401 }

427 void InitializeInstructionSequence(const CallDescriptor* call_descriptor) {
428 DCHECK_NULL(sequence_);
429 InstructionBlocks* instruction_blocks =
430 InstructionSequence::InstructionBlocksFor(instruction_zone(),
431 schedule());
432 sequence_ = instruction_zone()->New<InstructionSequence>(
433 isolate(), instruction_zone(), instruction_blocks);
434 if (call_descriptor && call_descriptor->RequiresFrameAsIncoming()) {
435 sequence_->instruction_blocks()[0]->mark_needs_frame();
436 } else {
437 DCHECK(call_descriptor->CalleeSavedFPRegisters().is_empty());
438 }
439 }
440
441 void InitializeFrameData(CallDescriptor* call_descriptor) {
442 DCHECK_NULL(frame_);
443 int fixed_frame_size = 0;
444 if (call_descriptor != nullptr) {
445 fixed_frame_size =
446 call_descriptor->CalculateFixedFrameSize(info()->code_kind());
447 }
448 frame_ = codegen_zone()->New<Frame>(fixed_frame_size, codegen_zone());
449 if (osr_helper_.has_value()) osr_helper()->SetupFrame(frame());
450 }
451
452 void InitializeRegisterAllocationData(const RegisterConfiguration* config,
453 CallDescriptor* call_descriptor) {
454 DCHECK_NULL(register_allocation_data_);
455 register_allocation_data_ =
456 register_allocation_zone()->New<RegisterAllocationData>(
457 config, register_allocation_zone(), frame(), sequence(),
458 &info()->tick_counter(), debug_name());
459 }
460
461 void InitializeOsrHelper() {
462 DCHECK(!osr_helper_.has_value());
463 osr_helper_.emplace(info());
464 }
465
466 void set_start_source_position(int position) {
467 DCHECK_EQ(start_source_position_, kNoSourcePosition);
468 start_source_position_ = position;
469 }
470
471 void InitializeCodeGenerator(Linkage* linkage) {
472 DCHECK_NULL(code_generator_);
473#if V8_ENABLE_WEBASSEMBLY
474 assembler_options_.is_wasm =
475 this->info()->IsWasm() || this->info()->IsWasmBuiltin();
476#endif
477 code_generator_ = new CodeGenerator(
478 codegen_zone(), frame(), linkage, sequence(), info(), isolate(),
479 osr_helper_, start_source_position_, jump_optimization_info_,
480 assembler_options(), info_->builtin(), max_unoptimized_frame_height(),
481 max_pushed_argument_count(),
482 v8_flags.trace_turbo_stack_accesses ? debug_name_.get() : nullptr);
483 }

600 // The maximal combined height of all inlined frames in their unoptimized
